### ==== FILES API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base route: /api/v1/files
#
# Upload lifecycle:
#   POST /api/v1/files → 202 Accepted (quarantined, ClamAV scan queued async)
#   GET  /api/v1/files/{id}/metadata → poll scan status (Quarantined → Available/Rejected)
#   GET  /api/v1/files/{id}          → download (Available files only)
#   DELETE /api/v1/files/{id}        → soft delete
#
# Max upload size: 100 MB
# Classification enum: Public, Internal, Confidential, Secret

# ── Upload ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Upload file (multipart/form-data)
# VS Code REST Client: use < syntax to attach a local file
# Replace ./sample.pdf with actual file path
# Required query params: tenantId, uploadedBy
# Optional: caseId (links file to a case), classification (default: Internal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/files?tenantId={{tenantId}}&uploadedBy=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&classification=Internal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------Boundary--

###

### Upload file linked to a case
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/files?tenantId={{tenantId}}&uploadedBy=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&caseId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&classification=Confidential
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="evidence.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./evidence.pdf
------Boundary--

# ── Metadata & Polling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get file metadata + virus scan status (poll after upload until status = Available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/metadata?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Download ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Download file (streaming, range-processing enabled)
# Returns 403 if file status is not Available (scan not passed yet)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}&requestedBy=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Delete ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Soft-delete a file record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/files/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?tenantId={{tenantId}}&deletedBy=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
